jparsec.util

Class Version

  • java.lang.Object
    • jparsec.util.Version

  • public class Version
extends java.lang.Object
    Version of the library.

    This class provides information about the current version of the library, by generating a Module object with the dependencies and their versions. This information is used by the JPARSEC Manager tool to automatically update the library and dependencies when the version of a given dependency changes.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    T. Alonso Albi - OAN (Spain)
